Feature: gmail

  Scenario: Send email on google chrome with attachment
    Given I am logged in to gmail on my homepage
    When I click on Compose
    And I add a recipient to my message
    And I add a subject to my message
    And I add an attachment to my message
    And I click Send
    Then the recipient receives the message with the right object and attachment
    
  Scenario: Send email on google chrome with different attachment and object
    Given I am logged in to gmail on my homepage
    When I click on Compose
    And I add a different recipient to my message
    And I add a different subject to my message
    And I add a different attachment to my message
    And I click Send
    Then the recipient receives the message with the right object and attachment
    
    Scenario: Send a new email with no subject to a recipient
    Given I am logged in on the gmail homepage
    When I click on Compose
    And add a recipient to my message
    And add an attachment to my message
    And I click Send
    Then a prompt window appears
    And I click Yes
    And the recipient receives the message with no subject and an attachment
    
   



